arts.ttl: The Lowdown on Bromley 3 Cheltenham Town 0 - Bromley cap off maiden EFL campaign with a drubbing
arts.sum: A Michael Cheek brace and a Nicke Kabamba finish provided Bromley a comfortable 3-0 win over Cheltenham Town on the final day of the League Two season. Bromley: Smith, Odutayo (Mayor 83), Elerewe, Sowunmi, Imray (Paul-Lavaly 60), Charles, Thompson Arthurs 71), Congreve (Ilunga 60), Whitely (Ifill 71), Kabamba, Cheek (Kader 83).
